1. *Grešim* kad mislim da mogu sve sama. (I'm mistaken when I think I can do everything by myself.)
2. *Grešiš* ako misliš da sam zaboravila naš dogovor. (You're mistaken if you think I forgot about our agreement.)
3. Ne *greši* se često, ali kad se greši, greši se veliko. (One doesn't make mistakes often, but when one does, they make big mistakes.)
4. Kad shvatim da sam *grešila*, uvek se trudim da ispravim svoju grešku. (When I realize I've made a mistake, I always try to correct it.)
5. Oni što nikada ne *greše* su obično oni koji ne rade ništa. (Those who never make mistakes are usually those who don't do anything.)
6. *Grešim* li ako kažem da je ovo jedna od najboljih knjiga koje sam ikada pročitala? (Am I wrong if I say that this is one of the best books I've ever read?)
7. Ne bih *grešio* kada bih rekao da je ovaj grad najlepši u ovo doba godine. (I wouldn't be mistaken if I said that this city is the most beautiful at this time of year.)
8. Često *grešimo* u proceni ljudi na prvi pogled. (We often make mistakes in judging people at first sight.)